## Key Insight from Brendan Hufford
Test organically first — scale with AI and ads second. 
The 272-day B2B buying journey requires sustained 
presence, not volume. 
Community-generated content (Figma's 10,000+ pages) 
represents the gold standard of AI-visible content — 
authentic, unique, and impossible to replicate.
